'''Pad 132''' was a docking bay in [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant's]] [[Subsector A45B12]]. Two weeks after the end of the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]], the ''[[Scimitar of Kelso]]'' left Pad 132 for [[Nar Shaddaa/Legends|Nar Shaddaa]].

